/**
 * Deep merges objects together, with some special rules: - Arrays are concatenated and de-duplicated unless {@link concatArrays | `concatArrays`} is `false`. - Objects are recursively merged. - `false` is only replaced with `true` - An object is never replaced with `true`, `false`, or `undefined`. - The original objects are not mutated. - `undefined` is always overwritten. - `0` is accepted.  @todo More options would be nice.
 */
